==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Adieu
<hw>A*dieu"</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>interj. & adv.</pos> <ety>[OE.
also <ets>adew</ets>, <ets>adewe</ets>, <ets>adue</ets>, F. <?/
<ets>dieu</ets>, fr. L. <ets>ad</ets> to + <ets>deus</ets> God.]</ety>
<def>Good-by; farewell; an expression of kind wishes at
